		<title>08Education</title>
		<content>     Three schools are situated in     
 Bedlinog.Graig Bedlinog Infants,      
 Bedlinog Infants and Bedlinog Junior  
 School.The total primary age pupils is
 approximately 155.All secondary school
 pupils attend Afon Taf Troedyrhiw,    
 except those who attend the Roman     
 Catholic School at Pontypridd and the 
 Welsh Secondary School at Rhydfelin.  
 Only in the last five years have      
 children had the opportunity of bi_   
 lingual schools and Roman Catholic    
 schools.                              
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
